Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.20,0:09:49.80,Default JP,,0,0,0,,なるほどねぇ......
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.20,0:09:49.80,Default CN,,0,0,0,,原来是这么一回事啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.80,0:09:52.17,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ひかりは  なんで怒らないポポ？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.80,0:09:52.17,Default CN,,0,0,0,,光她为什么不生气呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.40,0:09:53.75,Default JP,,0,0,0,,なんでって言われても...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.40,0:09:53.75,Default CN,,0,0,0,,你问为什么...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.37,0:09:57.12,Default JP,,0,0,0,,なぎさなんか  しょっちゅう怒って  もうウンザリメポ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.37,0:09:57.12,Default CN,,0,0,0,,渚成天都在生气 我已经受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.50,0:10:00.65,Default JP,,0,0,0,,うるさい！今の話に私は関係ないでしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.50,0:10:00.65,Default CN,,0,0,0,,你好烦啊！现在说的这事跟我没关系吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:05.57,Default JP,,0,0,0,,...仲がいいから怒るポポ？そうポポ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:05.57,Default CN,,0,0,0,,...感情好才会生气？是这样的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.77,0:10:08.77,Default JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8}はっきりそう言えることじゃないとは思うけど...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.77,0:10:08.77,Default CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8}也不全是这样的啦...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.40,0:10:11.12,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ほのか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.40,0:10:11.12,Default CN,,0,0,0,,穗乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.67,0:10:16.32,Default JP,,0,0,0,,でも  自分にとって大切な人が  本当に心配だったりすると
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.67,0:10:16.32,Default CN,,0,0,0,,重视你的人真的在担心你的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.50,0:10:18.89,Default JP,,0,0,0,,つい本気で怒ってしまうこともあるよね
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.50,0:10:18.89,Default CN,,0,0,0,,也可能会在无意间生气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.47,0:10:20.62,Default JP,,0,0,0,,大事なのは
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.47,0:10:20.62,Default CN,,0,0,0,,重要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.62,0:10:24.62,Default JP,,0,0,0,,お互いがお互いを  どう思ってるかってことじゃないかな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.62,0:10:24.62,Default CN,,0,0,0,,彼此抱有怎样的想法 不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.15,0:10:26.30,Default JP,,0,0,0,,そうだね
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.15,0:10:26.30,Default CN,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.02,0:10:30.85,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ポルン！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.02,0:10:30.85,Default CN,,0,0,0,,保伦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.32,0:10:41.57,Default JP,,0,0,0,,おまちどうさまです
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.32,0:10:41.57,Default CN,,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.87,0:10:43.07,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.87,0:10:43.07,Default CN,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.65,0:10:45.50,Default JP,,0,0,0,,お嬢ちゃん  何年生？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.65,0:10:45.50,Default CN,,0,0,0,,小妹妹 你读几年级啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:47.10,Default JP,,0,0,0,,中学1年生です
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:47.10,Default CN,,0,0,0,,初一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.22,0:10:49.65,Default JP,,0,0,0,,真面目にお手伝いして  偉いわねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.22,0:10:49.65,Default CN,,0,0,0,,这么努力帮忙 真不错呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.67,0:10:54.07,Default JP,,0,0,0,,いえね  私には小さい孫がいるんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.67,0:10:54.07,Default CN,,0,0,0,,跟你说啊 我也有一个小孙女
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.07,0:10:58.65,Default JP,,0,0,0,,あなたみたいに  素直で一生懸命な子に育ってくれたらいいなって
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.07,0:10:58.65,Default CN,,0,0,0,,要是她长大后也能像你一样懂事能干就好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.90,0:10:59.65,Default JP,,0,0,0,,そんな...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.90,0:10:59.65,Default CN,,0,0,0,,哪里...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.70,0:11:00.62,Default JP,,0,0,0,,私なんか...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.70,0:11:00.62,Default CN,,0,0,0,,我只是...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.62,0:11:02.27,Default JP,,0,0,0,,これからも頑張ってね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.62,0:11:02.27,Default CN,,0,0,0,,今后也要加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.89,0:11:05.17,Default JP,,0,0,0,,いつも美味しいたこ焼きを
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.89,0:11:05.17,Default CN,,0,0,0,,你们家的章鱼烧总是这么好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.17,0:11:06.22,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.17,0:11:06.22,Default CN,,0,0,0,,谢谢呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.92,0:11:08.00,Default JP,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.92,0:11:08.00,Default CN,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.00,0:11:12.10,Default JP,,0,0,0,,本当にどうも
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.00,0:11:12.10,Default CN,,0,0,0,,受您照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.75,0:11:14.05,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ありがとうございました
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.75,0:11:14.05,Default CN,,0,0,0,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.47,0:11:21.32,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ただいま
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.47,0:11:21.32,Default CN,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.52,0:11:22.62,Default JP,,0,0,0,,おかえりなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.52,0:11:22.62,Default CN,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.82,0:11:23.95,Default JP,,0,0,0,,たこ焼きの練習？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.82,0:11:23.95,Default CN,,0,0,0,,你在练习做章鱼烧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.50,0:11:25.10,Default JP,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.50,0:11:25.10,Default CN,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.97,0:11:27.47,Default JP,,0,0,0,,あの...アカネさん
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.97,0:11:27.47,Default CN,,0,0,0,,那个...茜姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.80,0:11:28.67,Default JP,,0,0,0,,なぁに？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.80,0:11:28.67,Default CN,,0,0,0,,怎么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.87,0:11:32.12,Default JP,,0,0,0,,私...アカネさんの力になりたいんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.87,0:11:32.12,Default CN,,0,0,0,,我...想帮上你的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.75,0:11:35.25,Default JP,,0,0,0,,何もできなくて...だから...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.75,0:11:35.25,Default CN,,0,0,0,,但我还什么都不会做...所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.50,0:11:38.30,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ひかりがここにいてくれるだけで  私は嬉しいの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.50,0:11:38.30,Default CN,,0,0,0,,只要你人在这 我就很高兴了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.72,0:11:44.92,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ほら  早くしないと  焦げちゃうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.72,0:11:44.92,Default CN,,0,0,0,,哎呀 你动作要快点 不然要烧焦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.92,0:11:45.47,Default JP,,0,0,0,,あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.92,0:11:45.47,Default CN,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.47,0:11:46.82,Default JP,,0,0,0,,本当だ  すいません
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.47,0:11:46.82,Default CN,,0,0,0,,真的焦了 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.17,0:11:48.92,Default JP,,0,0,0,,パフェも早く出さないと
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.17,0:11:48.92,Default CN,,0,0,0,,冰淇淋也要快点端出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.02,0:11:50.12,Default JP,,0,0,0,,あっ  忘れてた！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.02,0:11:50.12,Default CN,,0,0,0,,啊 我忘了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.25,0:11:55.23,Default JP,,0,0,0,,これ出してきちゃうね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.25,0:11:55.23,Default CN,,0,0,0,,我拿过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.95,0:11:57.47,Default JP,,0,0,0,,おまたせいたしました
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.95,0:11:57.47,Default CN,,0,0,0,,久等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.07,0:12:01.92,Default JP,,0,0,0,,アカネさん...お店やめないで
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.07,0:12:01.92,Default CN,,0,0,0,,茜姐...你一定不能把店收掉呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.57,0:12:07.20,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ポルンも手伝うポポ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.57,0:12:07.20,Default CN,,0,0,0,,我也要帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.57,0:12:08.57,Default JP,,0,0,0,,大丈夫よ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.57,0:12:08.57,Default CN,,0,0,0,,你不用帮忙也没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.70,0:12:10.72,Default JP,,0,0,0,,忙しいから  みんなと遊んでてね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.70,0:12:10.72,Default CN,,0,0,0,,我还要忙 你去跟她们玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.90,0:12:16.34,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ポルン！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.90,0:12:16.34,Default CN,,0,0,0,,保伦！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.37,0:12:18.32,Default JP,,0,0,0,,アカネさん
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.37,0:12:18.32,Default CN,,0,0,0,,茜姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.45,0:12:21.15,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ふたりとも来てたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.45,0:12:21.15,Default CN,,0,0,0,,你们两个来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.65,0:12:23.22,Default JP,,0,0,0,,アカネさん  あのね...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.65,0:12:23.22,Default CN,,0,0,0,,茜姐 那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.35,0:12:23.57,Default JP,,0,0,0,,えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.35,0:12:23.57,Default CN,,0,0,0,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.05,0:12:24.75,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ポルン
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.05,0:12:24.75,Default CN,,0,0,0,,保伦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.42,0:12:28.50,Default JP,,0,0,0,,何か悩みごとがあるんなら...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.42,0:12:28.50,Default CN,,0,0,0,,要是你有什么烦恼...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.10,0:12:31.64,Default JP,,0,0,0,,私達でよければ  お話だけでも...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.10,0:12:31.64,Default CN,,0,0,0,,如果你愿意 可以跟我们商量...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.15,0:12:34.12,Default JP,,0,0,0,,そのことなら  もう決めたから
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.15,0:12:34.12,Default CN,,0,0,0,,是要说那件事的话 我已经拿定主意了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.49,0:12:35.00,Default JP,,0,0,0,,えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.49,0:12:35.00,Default CN,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.90,0:12:36.82,Default JP,,0,0,0,,決めた...？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.90,0:12:36.82,Default CN,,0,0,0,,拿定主意了...？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.85,0:12:41.62,Default JP,,0,0,0,,こんにちは
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.85,0:12:41.62,Default CN,,0,0,0,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.70,0:12:43.77,Default JP,,0,0,0,,こんにちは
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.70,0:12:43.77,Default CN,,0,0,0,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.92,0:12:45.85,Default JP,,0,0,0,,こんにちは
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.92,0:12:45.85,Default CN,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.65,0:12:53.02,Default JP,,0,0,0,,決めたよ  答えは出た
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.65,0:12:53.02,Default CN,,0,0,0,,关于答复 我已经决定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.30,0:12:54.27,Default JP,,0,0,0,,先輩...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.30,0:12:54.27,Default CN,,0,0,0,,前辈...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.30,0:12:56.92,Default JP,,0,0,0,,頑張ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.30,0:12:56.92,Default CN,,0,0,0,,你要加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.30,0:12:57.65,Default JP,,0,0,0,,...じゃあ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.30,0:12:57.65,Default CN,,0,0,0,,...那你的意思就是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.42,0:13:09.05,Default JP,,0,0,0,,あんたはあんたの道を
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.42,0:13:09.05,Default CN,,0,0,0,,你走你的路
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.60,0:13:12.62,Default JP,,0,0,0,,私は私の道を
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.60,0:13:12.62,Default CN,,0,0,0,,我走我的路
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.92,0:13:22.05,Default JP,,0,0,0,,大丈夫  あんたなら  きっと上手くやれる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.92,0:13:22.05,Default CN,,0,0,0,,没事的 你肯定能做得来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.70,0:13:25.97,Default JP,,0,0,0,,私自身も  行けるところまで  つっ走ってみたいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.70,0:13:25.97,Default CN,,0,0,0,,我也会努力走下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.62,0:13:30.36,Default JP,,0,0,0,,自分で決めた道だから
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.62,0:13:30.36,Default CN,,0,0,0,,毕竟是我自己选的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.27,0:13:40.97,Default JP,,0,0,0,,この店は  私の夢の城
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.27,0:13:40.97,Default CN,,0,0,0,,这家店就是我梦想的城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.15,0:13:43.22,Default JP,,0,0,0,,たとえ今はどんなに小さくても
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.15,0:13:43.22,Default CN,,0,0,0,,就算现在还很小
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.30,0:13:47.25,Default JP,,0,0,0,,絶対に守りぬいて  いつかもっともっと大きく成長させてみせる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.30,0:13:47.25,Default CN,,0,0,0,,我也绝对会守住它 让它发展得越来越大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.85,0:13:48.92,Default JP,,0,0,0,,何より
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.85,0:13:48.92,Default CN,,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.92,0:13:52.55,Default JP,,0,0,0,,私達のたこ焼きを 楽しみに待ってくれる人たちのために
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.92,0:13:52.55,Default CN,,0,0,0,,这也是为了喜欢我们家章鱼烧的客人们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.22,0:13:55.42,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ねっ？ひかり？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.22,0:13:55.42,Default CN,,0,0,0,,对吧？光？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.52,0:13:58.26,Default JP,,0,0,0,,うん！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.52,0:13:58.26,Default CN,,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.02,0:14:04.68,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ありがとうございました  先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.02,0:14:04.68,Default CN,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.17,0:14:10.07,Default JP,,0,0,0,,本当は最初から  そう言われるだろうなって覚悟はしてたんです
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.17,0:14:10.07,Default CN,,0,0,0,,其实 我一开始就做好了被你拒绝的思想准备
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.25,0:14:12.15,Default JP,,0,0,0,,だけどなんか  吹っ切れました
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.25,0:14:12.15,Default CN,,0,0,0,,所以 现在我反倒觉得如释重负呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.80,0:14:16.00,Default JP,,0,0,0,,僕も先輩に負けないくらい  素晴しい仕事してみせます
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.80,0:14:16.00,Default CN,,0,0,0,,我会加油干的 一定不输给前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.32,0:14:18.54,Default JP,,0,0,0,,中尾くん...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.32,0:14:18.54,Default CN,,0,0,0,,中尾...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.72,0:14:24.50,Default JP,,0,0,0,,そうだ  もうひとつのお願いのほうは...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.72,0:14:24.50,Default CN,,0,0,0,,对了 我的另一个请求...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.65,0:14:26.92,Default JP,,0,0,0,,あ  あっ！時間ないって  言ってたよね！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.65,0:14:26.92,Default CN,,0,0,0,,哎 哎呀！时间有点紧迫呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.92,0:14:28.13,Default JP,,0,0,0,,続きは  歩きながら！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.92,0:14:28.13,Default CN,,0,0,0,,我们边走边说吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.95,0:14:30.60,Default JP,,0,0,0,,あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.95,0:14:30.60,Default CN,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.75,0:14:32.17,Default JP,,0,0,0,,しっかり  店番お願いね！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.75,0:14:32.17,Default CN,,0,0,0,,要好好看店啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.65,0:14:33.82,Default JP,,0,0,0,,...は  はい！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.65,0:14:33.82,Default CN,,0,0,0,,...知 知道了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.45,0:14:36.13,Default JP,,0,0,0,,い  いってらっしゃーい...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.45,0:14:36.13,Default CN,,0,0,0,,您 您慢走...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.55,0:14:38.22,Default JP,,0,0,0,,いってきまーす
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.55,0:14:38.22,Default CN,,0,0,0,,我先走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.65,0:14:40.75,Default JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8}デ  デートくらいいいじゃないスか？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.65,0:14:40.75,Default CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs35}就 就约个会嘛 这没什么吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.75,0:14:42.62,Default JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8}そ  その話はまた今度...！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.75,0:14:42.62,Default CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs35}下 下次再说...！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.80,0:14:44.95,Default JP,,0,0,0,,よかった...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.80,0:14:44.95,Default CN,,0,0,0,,太好了...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.00,0:14:46.92,Default JP,,0,0,0,,あっ  ポルン！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.00,0:14:46.92,Default CN,,0,0,0,,对了 保伦！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.92,0:14:47.55,Default JP,,0,0,0,,えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.92,0:14:47.55,Default CN,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:49.72,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ポルン
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:49.72,Default CN,,0,0,0,,保伦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.72,0:14:51.02,Default JP,,0,0,0,,どこなのー
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.72,0:14:51.02,Default CN,,0,0,0,,你在哪里啊——
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.32,0:14:52.57,Default JP,,0,0,0,,邪悪な気配メポ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.32,0:14:52.57,Default CN,,0,0,0,,是邪恶的气息！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.57,0:14:53.87,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ミップルも感じるミポ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.57,0:14:53.87,Default CN,,0,0,0,,我也感受到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.30,0:15:02.27,Default JP,,0,0,0,,出た！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.30,0:15:02.27,Default CN,,0,0,0,,出现了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.42,0:15:03.37,Default JP,,0,0,0,,なぎさ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.42,0:15:03.37,Default CN,,0,0,0,,渚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:05.25,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ほのか  いくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:05.25,Default CN,,0,0,0,,要上了 穗乃香
Dialogue: 1,0:15:16.67,0:15:20.00,White,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\clip(m 200 670 l 750 670 750 700 200 700)}Dual Aurora Wave
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.67,0:15:20.00,Black,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\iclip(m 200 670 l 750 670 750 700 200 700)}Dual Aurora Wave
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.10,0:15:31.07,Default JP,,0,0,0,,光の使者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.10,0:15:31.07,Default CN,,0,0,0,,光之使者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.37,0:15:32.70,Black,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\bord5\b0\be5}Cure Black
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.95,0:15:34.95,Default JP,,0,0,0,,光の使者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.95,0:15:34.95,Default CN,,0,0,0,,光之使者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.22,0:15:36.67,White,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\bord5\b0\be5}Cure White
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.87,0:15:40.59,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ふたりはプリキュア！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.87,0:15:40.59,Default CN,,0,0,0,,我们两人是Precure！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.15,0:15:44.17,Default JP,,0,0,0,,闇の力の僕たちよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.15,0:15:44.17,Default CN,,0,0,0,,黑暗力量的奴仆们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.35,0:15:47.47,Default JP,,0,0,0,,とっととお家に  帰りなさい！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.35,0:15:47.47,Default CN,,0,0,0,,还不快点给我滚回老家去！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.30,0:15:51.42,Default JP,,0,0,0,,今日は  お前達の相手をしている暇はない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.30,0:15:51.42,Default CN,,0,0,0,,今天我没空对付你们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.32,0:15:53.96,Default JP,,0,0,0,,あの娘を出せ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.32,0:15:53.96,Default CN,,0,0,0,,把那个小姑娘交出来！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.72,0:15:58.05,Default JP,,0,0,0,,...それって  ひかりのこと？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.72,0:15:58.05,Default CN,,0,0,0,,...你是在说光？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.65,0:16:01.35,Default JP,,0,0,0,,悪いけど  ここから先は行かせない！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.65,0:16:01.35,Default CN,,0,0,0,,那可抱歉了 我们不会让你过去的！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.30,0:16:36.97,Default JP,,0,0,0,,どこ行っちゃったのかしら...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.30,0:16:36.97,Default CN,,0,0,0,,跑哪去了...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.70,0:16:38.65,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ポルン...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.70,0:16:38.65,Default CN,,0,0,0,,保伦...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.30,0:16:44.87,Default JP,,0,0,0,,どこにもいない...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.30,0:16:44.87,Default CN,,0,0,0,,哪里都找不到...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.93,0:16:49.47,Default JP,,0,0,0,,何  これ？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.93,0:16:49.47,Default CN,,0,0,0,,什么情况？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.25,0:16:53.00,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ど  どうしたの？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.25,0:16:53.00,Default CN,,0,0,0,,怎 怎么了这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.00,0:16:54.60,Default JP,,0,0,0,,一体  何があったの？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.00,0:16:54.60,Default CN,,0,0,0,,到底发生了什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.60,0:16:56.07,Default JP,,0,0,0,,できたポポ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.60,0:16:56.07,Default CN,,0,0,0,,做好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.10,0:16:58.07,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ひかり
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.10,0:16:58.07,Default CN,,0,0,0,,光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.40,0:16:59.85,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ポルンできたポポ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.40,0:16:59.85,Default CN,,0,0,0,,我做出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.55,0:17:01.17,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ポルン！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.55,0:17:01.17,Default CN,,0,0,0,,保伦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.00,0:17:03.75,Default JP,,0,0,0,,イタズラしたら駄目じゃない！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.00,0:17:03.75,Default CN,,0,0,0,,不可以恶作剧啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.75,0:17:04.60,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ごめんポポ...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.75,0:17:04.60,Default CN,,0,0,0,,对不起...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.86,0:17:07.33,Default JP,,0,0,0,,それに  急にいなくなったりして！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.86,0:17:07.33,Default CN,,0,0,0,,而且你还突然玩失踪！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.92,0:17:09.50,Default JP,,0,0,0,,...怒ってくれて
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.92,0:17:09.50,Default CN,,0,0,0,,...你生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.82,0:17:11.30,Default JP,,0,0,0,,嬉しいポポ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.82,0:17:11.30,Default CN,,0,0,0,,我好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.97,0:17:13.00,Default JP,,0,0,0,,...どうして？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.97,0:17:13.00,Default CN,,0,0,0,,...为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.00,0:17:16.90,Default JP,,0,0,0,,本気で怒ってくれるのは  仲良しのしるしポポ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.00,0:17:16.90,Default CN,,0,0,0,,会真的生气 说明感情好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.25,0:17:18.35,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ポルン...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.25,0:17:18.35,Default CN,,0,0,0,,保伦...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.97,0:17:22.45,Default JP,,0,0,0,,私  自分の気持ちに精一杯で
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.97,0:17:22.45,Default CN,,0,0,0,,我只顾着自己
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.57,0:17:24.05,Default JP,,0,0,0,,かまってあげられなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.57,0:17:24.05,Default CN,,0,0,0,,没能考虑到你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.05,0:17:25.22,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ごめんね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.05,0:17:25.22,Default CN,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.85,0:17:31.80,Default JP,,0,0,0,,もっともっと  ひかりと仲良くなりたいポポ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.85,0:17:31.80,Default CN,,0,0,0,,我想跟光你变得更加亲密
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.51,0:17:31.80,Default CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}“ひかり（光）”
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.55,0:17:43.72,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ポルン...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.55,0:17:43.72,Default CN,,0,0,0,,保伦...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.42,0:17:45.72,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ありがとう...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.42,0:17:45.72,Default CN,,0,0,0,,谢谢你...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.00,0:17:55.10,Default JP,,0,0,0,,な  何あのパワー...？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.00,0:17:55.10,Default CN,,0,0,0,,这 这什么怪力啊...？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.40,0:17:56.61,Default JP,,0,0,0,,それに  速い！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.40,0:17:56.61,Default CN,,0,0,0,,而且 速度也很快！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.87,0:17:59.62,Default JP,,0,0,0,,やめて！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.87,0:17:59.62,Default CN,,0,0,0,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.65,0:18:01.50,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ひかり！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.65,0:18:01.50,Default CN,,0,0,0,,光！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.52,0:18:14.62,Hikari,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\b0}Luminous Shining Stream
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.15,0:18:41.32,Default JP,,0,0,0,,輝く命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.15,0:18:41.32,Default CN,,0,0,0,,闪耀的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.52,0:18:43.30,Hikari,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\b0}Shiny Luminous
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.25,0:18:46.30,Default JP,,0,0,0,,光の心と光の意志
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.25,0:18:46.30,Default CN,,0,0,0,,光之心与光之意志啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.92,0:18:48.80,Default JP,,0,0,0,,全てをひとつにするために！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.92,0:18:48.80,Default CN,,0,0,0,,让一切合而为一吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.70,0:18:57.35,Default JP,,0,0,0,,やっと出てきたな！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.70,0:18:57.35,Default CN,,0,0,0,,总算出现了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.75,0:19:00.80,Default JP,,0,0,0,,お前の力がいかほどのものか  見せてもらおう！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.75,0:19:00.80,Default CN,,0,0,0,,就让我领教领教 你到底有多少斤两吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.27,0:19:02.40,Default JP,,0,0,0,,こっちへ来ないで！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.27,0:19:02.40,Default CN,,0,0,0,,不要过来！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.47,0:19:05.87,Default JP,,0,0,0,,この店には  指一本触れさせない！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.47,0:19:05.87,Default CN,,0,0,0,,我不会让你伤到这家店的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.55,0:19:11.40,Default JP,,0,0,0,,なんだ？そんなものが大切なのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.55,0:19:11.40,Default CN,,0,0,0,,怎么？你这么宝贝这家店吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.85,0:19:14.10,Default JP,,0,0,0,,われわれにはなんの価値もない！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.85,0:19:14.10,Default CN,,0,0,0,,这对我们来说毫无价值！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.60,0:19:16.45,Default JP,,0,0,0,,あなたにとって価値はなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.60,0:19:16.45,Default CN,,0,0,0,,对你们来说是毫无价值
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.60,0:19:18.51,Default JP,,0,0,0,,あたし達にとっては宝物なの！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.60,0:19:18.51,Default CN,,0,0,0,,对我们来说却是无价的宝物！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.77,0:19:21.70,Default JP,,0,0,0,,アカネさんと私の  夢のお城なのよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.77,0:19:21.70,Default CN,,0,0,0,,这是茜姐和我的 梦想的城堡啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.22,0:19:24.37,Default JP,,0,0,0,,面白い
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.22,0:19:24.37,Default CN,,0,0,0,,有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.50,0:19:26.62,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ならば  粉々にしてやる！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.50,0:19:26.62,Default CN,,0,0,0,,那大爷我就要把它给砸掉！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.77,0:19:28.77,Default JP,,0,0,0,,やめて！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.77,0:19:28.77,Default CN,,0,0,0,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.07,0:19:29.77,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ルミナス！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.07,0:19:29.77,Default CN,,0,0,0,,Luminous！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.05,0:19:49.95,Default JP,,0,0,0,,お  俺を止めた...？！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.05,0:19:49.95,Default CN,,0,0,0,,居 居然能挡下我...？！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.37,0:19:51.75,Default JP,,0,0,0,,タコカフェは...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.37,0:19:51.75,Default CN,,0,0,0,,这家章鱼咖啡...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.75,0:19:54.65,Default JP,,0,0,0,,私とアカネさんの  宝物なの！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.75,0:19:54.65,Default CN,,0,0,0,,是我和茜姐的宝物啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.95,0:20:07.35,Black,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\bord5\b0\be5}Black Thunder
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.15,0:20:09.77,White,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\bord5\b0\be5}White Thunder
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.72,0:20:19.55,Default JP,,0,0,0,,プリキュアの美しき魂が
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.72,0:20:19.55,Default CN,,0,0,0,,以Precure之美丽灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.90,0:20:22.32,Default JP,,0,0,0,,邪悪な心を打ち砕く！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.90,0:20:22.32,Default CN,,0,0,0,,于此将邪恶之心粉碎！
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.30,0:20:26.87,White,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\clip(m 200 670 l 750 670 750 700 200 700)}Precure Marble Screw
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.30,0:20:26.87,Black,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\iclip(m 200 670 l 750 670 750 700 200 700)}Precure Marble Screw
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.55,0:20:32.17,White,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\clip(m 200 670 l 750 670 750 700 200 700)}Max
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.55,0:20:32.17,Black,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\iclip(m 200 670 l 750 670 750 700 200 700)}Max
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.97,0:20:53.10,Default JP,,0,0,0,,えっ？これポルンが作ったの？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.97,0:20:53.10,Default CN,,0,0,0,,欸？这是保伦做的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.70,0:20:55.08,Default JP,,0,0,0,,凄いじゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.70,0:20:55.08,Default CN,,0,0,0,,厉害了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.45,0:20:57.20,Default JP,,0,0,0,,美味しいよ  このチョコパフェ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.45,0:20:57.20,Default CN,,0,0,0,,这巧克力冰淇淋巨好吃啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.20,0:20:58.85,Default JP,,0,0,0,,仲良しパフェポポ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.20,0:20:58.85,Default CN,,0,0,0,,这是友谊的冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.00,0:20:59.85,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ねぇ？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.00,0:20:59.85,Default CN,,0,0,0,,对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.15,0:21:00.81,Default JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8}悪い  悪い
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.15,0:21:00.81,Default CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8}抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.80,0:21:02.90,Default JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8}すっかり遅くなっちゃって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.80,0:21:02.90,Default CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8}我回来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.45,0:21:05.50,Default JP,,0,0,0,,何か  困ったことでもあった？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.45,0:21:05.50,Default CN,,0,0,0,,怎么 你们在想什么烦心事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.85,0:21:07.82,Default JP,,0,0,0,,何にもありません！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.85,0:21:07.82,Default CN,,0,0,0,,没有 什么也没有！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.40,0:21:09.57,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ならいいんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.40,0:21:09.57,Default CN,,0,0,0,,那就行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.57,0:21:11.82,Default JP,,0,0,0,,今日は疲れちゃったから  店じまいしちゃうね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.57,0:21:11.82,Default CN,,0,0,0,,今天也挺累的了 就提早收摊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.50,0:21:14.71,Default JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8}あーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.50,0:21:14.71,Default CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8}卧槽——！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.97,0:21:17.37,Default JP,,0,0,0,,なんで  こんなに散らかってるのよ？！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.97,0:21:17.37,Default CN,,0,0,0,,为什么会乱成这样啊？！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.92,0:21:20.18,Default JP,,0,0,0,,なぎさ！あんた何やってんのよ？！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.92,0:21:20.18,Default CN,,0,0,0,,渚！你干了什么好事？！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.67,0:21:22.47,Default JP,,0,0,0,,えっ？なんで？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.67,0:21:22.47,Default CN,,0,0,0,,欸？为什么怪我？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.20,0:21:24.47,Default JP,,0,0,0,,なぎささん！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.20,0:21:24.47,Default CN,,0,0,0,,渚！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.17,0:21:25.87,Default JP,,0,0,0,,パフェ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.17,0:21:25.87,Default CN,,0,0,0,,冰淇淋呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.24,0:21:27.10,Default JP,,0,0,0,,えっ？！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.24,0:21:27.10,Default CN,,0,0,0,,欸？！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.10,0:21:28.35,Default JP,,0,0,0,,あたし？！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.10,0:21:28.35,Default CN,,0,0,0,,这锅要我来背吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.25,0:21:33.32,Default JP,,0,0,0,,...三十六計  逃げるが先！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.25,0:21:33.32,Default CN,,0,0,0,,...三十六计 拔腿就跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.80,0:21:36.32,Default JP,,0,0,0,,...それを言うなら「逃げるが勝ち」よ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.80,0:21:36.32,Default CN,,0,0,0,,...是“走为上计”才对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.32,0:21:38.12,Default JP,,0,0,0,,さいなら！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.32,0:21:38.12,Default CN,,0,0,0,,溜了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.92,0:21:40.15,Default JP,,0,0,0,,コラ！待て！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.92,0:21:40.15,Default CN,,0,0,0,,喂！别跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.57,0:21:43.95,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ちょっと  なぎさ！待ちなさいってば！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.57,0:21:43.95,Default CN,,0,0,0,,渚你这个兔崽子！给我站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.47,0:21:45.90,Default JP,,0,0,0,,でも  よかった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.47,0:21:45.90,Default CN,,0,0,0,,不过 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.90,0:21:47.51,Default JP,,0,0,0,,みんな元気になって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.90,0:21:47.51,Default CN,,0,0,0,,大家又变得有精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.12,0:21:52.20,Default JP,,0,0,0,,綺麗...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.12,0:21:52.20,Default CN,,0,0,0,,真漂亮啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.67,0:21:55.70,Default JP,,0,0,0,,もうすぐ  新しい季節の始まりね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.67,0:21:55.70,Default CN,,0,0,0,,新的季节很快就要到了呢
